flowchart TD
    title Data Flow: Движение данных в AI Day Planner Agent

    User([Пользователь]) -->|Текст или JSON| Server[FastAPI Server]

    User -->|POST /api/chat| ChatEndpoint[POST /api/chat]
    User -->|POST /api/plan| PlanEndpoint[POST /api/plan]

    ChatEndpoint --> Guard[Guardrail Check]
    PlanEndpoint --> Guard

    Guard -->|injection?| Reject[Reject: 500]
    Guard -->|OK| NLP[NLP Parser: extract_tasks]
    PlanEndpoint --> Anonymizer[Анонимизация PII]
    NLP --> Anonymizer

    Anonymizer -->|Очищенные задачи| Agent[Agent Core]

    subgraph ReAct цикл
        Agent -->|think: system prompt + tasks| LLM[LLM Function Calling]
        LLM -->|tool_calls| ToolExec[tool_execute]

        ToolExec -->|get_current_time| TimeResult[Текущее время]
        ToolExec -->|get_date(offset)| DateResult[Дата]
        ToolExec -->|get_events(date)| CalRead[Чтение календаря]
        ToolExec -->|validate_schedule(plan)| ValidationResult[Валидация плана]
        ToolExec -->|create_event(...)| CalWrite[Создание события]

        TimeResult --> LLM
        DateResult --> LLM
        CalRead --> LLM
        ValidationResult --> LLM
        CalWrite --> LLM
    end

    Agent -->|План завершён| Evals[Evaluate Quality]
    Evals -->|quality_score| Metrics[MetricsCollector]
    Agent -->|Трейс| Langfuse[(Langfuse Cloud)]
    Metrics -->|Сохранение| MetricsFile[metrics.json]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrape /metrics каждые 10с| Server
    Grafana[(Grafana)] -->|запрос метрик| Prometheus

    Agent -->|Результат| Server
    Server -->|JSON с планом и метриками| User
